title: Steph’s Apex Mountain Leaves Boston Reeling With Rob Mahoney and Wosny Lambre
description:
The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Wosny Lambre and Rob Mahoney to discuss the Warriors' series-tying win in Boston, Steph Curry’s incredible performance, Jaylen Brown shining as Jayson Tatum struggles, a look ahead to Game 5, and more.

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Wosny Lambre and Rob Mahoney
Producer: Kyle Crichton
